{"tid":1947542,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"三日兩夜 傳嘉莉","createTime":"2020-03-28T11:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T14:56:57.000Z","uid":38456,"like":2,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"fca6501d6a128a1b35946b715ab7fac4c90f9d56","tid":1947542,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"3日2夜[粵]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n傅嘉莉踏上柬埔寨散心之旅，巧遇攝影發燒友楊潮凱，一起發掘金邊必到打卡位！到訪宏偉的金邊皇宮，謹記捕捉宮殿的Magic Hour留影。再參加海上巡航，觀賞最美麗的落霞。他們置身精品酒店的無邊際泳池暢泳，悠閒自在；然後到中央市場尋寶，聞名世界的貢布胡椒、茉莉香米有何特別？潮凱帶路品嚐正宗柬埔寨菜，傳統烤雞、青胡椒法式燉蛋吃出獨有滋味，二人更膽粗粗食螞蟻？飯後在商場遊樂場激玩一番，度過完美晚上。"},{"pid":"5446f5a439d90e82a16b97684c03f9394c4e41e2","tid":1947542,"uid":310700,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"CCTVB 打手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf7b4e67f1be99839e8f0238a03738a9b332f61","tid":1947542,"uid":38301,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - New_God_美斯 )<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"d5c5694b6f7c5868719aa6e0e4c0a6c1fb6ac989","tid":1947542,"uid":412,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:17:05.000Z","msg":"樓主躝啦<br />\n厚臉皮到老母畀人任屌唔嬲"},{"pid":"33319ca61a35f6349a7a55a373103fd00b3bf0cf","tid":1947542,"uid":149494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"佢同Twice個Mina好似樣"},{"pid":"4106f764a18236df065c939d1e814bfb8d4aac17","tid":1947542,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"真心幾正 不過拉"},{"pid":"ea3b8880856f15c22389e28d6206b17e83dd3664","tid":1947542,"uid":317378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"仲tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f